装修，凭啥我要出去租房子<br /><br />无解", "last_modified": 1632455752, "replies": 109, "id": 803878}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1620106980", "name": "linux", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1620106980", "title": "Linux", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux", "topics": 6340, "footer": "", "header": "Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1620106980", "stars": 5607, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "dante6733", "website": "aiops.com", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d501/0155/368833_mini.png?m=1631322859", "bio": "人工智能让运维更加高效！\r\n智能告警，智能事件，智能监控！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dante6733", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1544171654, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d501/0155/368833_mini.png?m=1631322859", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d501/0155/368833_mini.png?m=1631322859", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 368833}, "last_reply_by": "lucybenz", "last_touched": 1632516480, "title": "一个运维可以管理 5 万台服务器吗？怎么管？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/803912", "created": 1632464321, "content": "理性讨论，如果有 5 万台服务器，虚拟机和物理机都行，一个人能管好吗？如果一个人管不好，那怎么管？\r\n\r\n有没有大佬有这么多台服务器的管理经验？也希望能够分享一下经验，改进大家的运维效率。", "content_rendered": "<p>理性讨论，如果有 5 万台服务器，虚拟机和物理机都行，一个人能管好吗？如果一个人管不好，那怎么管？</p>\n<p>有没有大佬有这么多台服务器的管理经验？也希望能够分享一下经验，改进大家的运维效率。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1632464321, "replies": 97, "id": 803912}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_large.png?m=1591791660", "name": "gts", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_normal.png?m=1591791660", "title": "全球工单系统", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/gts", "topics": 8485, "footer": "", "header": "希望这里能够